    • Field Detail

      • batteryTimeToEmpty

        public int batteryTimeToEmpty
        The remaining capacity of the battery in minutes. The default value -1 is assigned when this parameter not requested or failed to get it.

      • batteryStateOfCharge

        public int batteryStateOfCharge
        The predicted Battery capacity in terms of Percentage. The default value -1 is assigned when this parameter not requested or failed to get it.

      • batteryStateOfHealth

        public int batteryStateOfHealth
        Battery health in percentage. State of Health (SOH) is the battery capacity as Percentage of the battery rated capacity. The default value -1 is assigned when this parameter not requested or failed to get it.

      • batteryChargingTime

        public int batteryChargingTime
        The remaining time needed for the terminal to be in cradle to reach capacity that will be enough for a requested duration of shopping trip. The default value -1 is assigned when this parameter not requested or failed to get it. If Device is not charging , then this parameter is not available and displays 65535. Note: This parameter is not supported now. Hence returns 0xFFFFh(65535)

      • batteryChargingTimeElapsed

        public int batteryChargingTimeElapsed
        The duration in minutes in which battery was charged during the current charge cycle. The default value -1 is assigned when this parameter not requested or failed to get it. If Device is not charging , then this parameter is not available and displays 65535

      • timeSinceBatteryReplaced

        public int timeSinceBatteryReplaced
        The duration in days battery was last replaced. The default value -1 is assigned when this parameter not requested or failed to get it.

      • timeSinceReboot

        public int timeSinceReboot
        The time in minutes since the device cold booted the last time. The default value -1 is assigned when this parameter not requested or failed to get it.

      • batteryDateOfManufacture

        public String batteryDateOfManufacture
        The manufacture date of the battery in the format year/mm/date. Empty string is assigned when this parameter not request or failed to get it.
